CatDescriptText: The Sergeant William F. Carney VFW Post No. 46 was located at 609 Duff Street in the Hill.  Joe Louis served in the U.S. Army from 1942 to 1946, touring the country as an army boxing instructor.
TitMainTitle: Joe Louis wearing U.S. Army sergeant's uniform, looking at battle scene print over mantelpiece possibly in Carney VFW post, 609 Duff Street, Hill District
